Mail Sender is an Spring Application which allows you to send emails with msg/attachment using spring. 
In application.properties file, username refers to <your email>. and password refers to the app password you created in security tab of google.
If you don't have a app password, create a new app password. before that you must turn on the 2step verification.

while running the application, if you got any exception like connection time out, please check the port numbers,
username, password, and the location.
